Magic Box Project
---------------------------------------------------------------
by Alexander Rulkens, studio:ludens
http://www.studioludens.com/
http://www.alexrulkens.com/

A programmatic IDE for generating 2D parametric designs for 
lasercutting, milling and graphic design. 

Created in AS3

We are planning a port to Javascript. If you want to help, please
contact us at info@magic-box.org

---------------------------------------------------------------
FEATURES
---------------------------------------------------------------

Magic Box implements the SVG path drawing instructions and
adds a programming layer on top of that.

It does this by giving the user the possibility to create
variables, control structures, lists and functions. 

In this way, a designer is able to create a design template that
can be easily changed by an end user to suit its needs.



